OL,6,FA hit and run driver who seriously
OL,7,Finjured a young boy and his sister in
OL,8,FKings Heath has been jailed.
OL,10,FShahbaz Khan failed to stop his car
OL,11,Fafter hitting the pair.
OL,13,FKhan drove at speeds of over 60mph
OL,14,Fdespite being in a 20mph zone in Kings
OL,15,FHeath High Street, with CCTV footage
OL,16,Fshowing him travelling through the red
OL,17,Flight of the pedestrian crossing and
OL,18,Fhitting the boy and his sister.
