OL,4,C20mph zone jailed after hit and run
OL,6,FThey were taken to hospital with
OL,7,Fserious injuries, with the young boy,
OL,8,F8, suffering two broken legs and a
OL,9,Fhead injury, while his sister, 21,
OL,10,Fsuffered a broken leg, fractured
OL,11,Fpelvis and a head injury.
OL,13,FThe crash has left both survivors
OL,14,Fliving with the physical and
OL,15,Fpsychological impact of their
OL,16,Finjuries, more than 12 months on from
OL,17,Fthe incident.
