OL,4,C20mph zone jailed after hit and run
OL,6,FImmediately after hitting the siblings
OL,7,Fwith his car, Khan attempted to flee
OL,8,Fthe scene, but a member of the public
OL,9,Fsaw him and took a photo of the 29-
OL,10,Fyear-old and his car.
OL,12,FKhan, of Park Road, Birmingham, was
OL,13,Fjailed for two years eight months at
OL,14,FBirmingham Crown Court on 28 August.
