OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Paul Hughes from
OL,7,Fthe Serious Collision Investigation
OL,8,FUnit said:"We had two vulnerable road
OL,9,Fusers who showed common sense and good
OL,10,Froad safety awareness and chose to use
OL,11,Fa pedestrian crossing correctly which
OL,12,Fhad been placed there to afford them
OL,13,Fthe protection they deserve.
OL,15,F"Sadly the actions of one individual
OL,16,Fthat day changed their lives forever.
